# Expected Deliverables

Implement a reusable component located at:

```
resources/views/components/sections/statistics.blade.php
```

Update the homepage to consume this component.

The homepage Blade should become cleaner without changing its visual output.

Example:

```blade
<x-sections.statistics :page="$page" />
```

or

```blade
<x-sections.statistics
    :statistics="$statistics"
/>
```

Choose whichever produces the cleanest architecture.

